 TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Hdt.\">Hdt.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.175</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Χῖος λ.</foreign> a <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">tonsure</tr_> in the middle of the head, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg4083.tlg001:1462:38\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Eust.\">Eust.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1462.38</biblScope></bibl>. </sense> <sense n=\"4\" id=\"n63960.5\" level=\"3\" opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"sense\"> of large fishes, <xr opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"xr\"> <lbl opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"lbl\">=</lbl> <ref targOrder=\"U\" lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"ref\">λοφιά</ref></xr>, <bibl default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Plu.</author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.978a</biblScope></bibl>.</sense> </entryFree>"}]}